# Project contract

Treat [README.md](mdc:README.md) and [SYSTEM_DESIGN.md](mdc:SYSTEM_DESIGN.md) as architecture sources. Milestones: [docs/ROADMAP.md](mdc:docs/ROADMAP.md).

## Repos

- **auth-service** — sibling repo (`../auth-service`), not inside blog-cms.
- **blog-cms** — gateway, blog, media, audit, frontend, deploy.

## Boundaries

- Each service has its **own MongoDB logical database** (`blog`, `audit`, auth in auth repo).
- **Phase 1 VPS:** Mongo + apps; no Redpanda unless `KAFKA_ENABLED=true`.
- Auth integrates via REST/JWT only; no Kafka in auth-service.
